<br>
The only stated reason I ever saw for why they did this was simply to prevent you from dying when zoning, because people were very upset that they zoned with HPs but ended up dying and taking XP loss any way.<br>
<br>
Instead of really looking at the problem and reordering the way a player is constructed when entering a zone, they just stripped all buffs (not even restricted to HP buffs!) when you leave a zone and your current HP are less than HP from buffs/items.  That is a really, really sloppy fix and one that would only stand in a product like a MMORPG or a Microsoft OS/App.<br>
<br>
