<br>
I only found this out the hard way recently, when a chanter with an air stone asked me for a ride to PoS from Skyfire. She was offering KEI (which had expired for me) so I said &quot;sure!&quot;. She buffed me with KEI, gave me the rock, and I ported her up. I said goodbye, thanked her, and jumped off. As I landed in the water near FP, I thought, &quot;you know... it seems awfully dark here today.&quot;<br>
<br>
My chill sight was gone. Doh! THen I looked, and noticed ALL my buffs were gone! DOH DOH!<br>
<br>
I sent her a tell and she said she forgot she was supposed to buff me *after* the port.<br>
