<br>
When you zone, your character is basically naked, then all the gear added back to it. If you had 175 HP from gear, and you zoned with 90 HP left, when the server zones you naked, you have negative HP, so you are technically dead. Verant coded a check for this, because you shouldn't be able to die while zoning. But since they always code things backwards, you died, you lost your buffs, but since you can't die while zoning, they put you on the other side with 0 hp + HP from gear.<br>
<br>
A reason for this was also given about a corpse dupe bug. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=asos>Asos</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://saedyan.freeservers.com/images/pstgif.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(9/21/02 8:02:05 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=20837.topic&index=15>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://saedyan.freeservers.com/images/pstgif.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Zones that strip buffs</span><hr size=1> Wow, im not reading all the retarded make belief answers because the first few were totally made up. The exact reason, which was stated by Verant, is in case you have been DOTed, and zone with not alot of HP, it strips all of your buffs so the DOT is gone. The reason they did this was mainly due to Rallos Zek (back before the other Zeks were out). They said they had to do so becuase some people were loosing their corpses on rare occasions. People would zone with a dot, and die while zoning, but not be in a zone, and the body would poof. This could easily be reversed by a GM (as it happened to me on RZ back in the day). <p><BR><center><img src=http://www.ketelkaotic.com/asos2.jpg><br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=193831"> My Profile</a><br></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/useverinewolfe.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Severine Wolfe</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br> <font color=#ffffff